---
import GuideLayout from '../layouts/GuideLayout.astro';
import { SITE } from '../lib/site';

const lastUpdated = 'May 25, 2026';
---

<GuideLayout
  title="Disclaimer"
  description="Editorial and content disclaimer for n8n.gjam.in. Workflows, guides, and comparisons are for informational use; test before deploying to production."
  path="/disclaimer"
  breadcrumbs={[
    { name: 'Home', path: '/' },
    { name: 'Disclaimer', path: '/disclaimer' },
  ]}
  datePublished="2025-01-01"
>
  <p><em>Last updated: {lastUpdated}</em></p>

  <h2>Informational only</h2>
  <p>
    Content on <strong>{SITE.name}</strong> — including workflow files, guides, comparisons, and
    code snippets — is published for educational and informational purposes. It is not professional
    advice. Always test workflows and configuration changes in a staging environment before running
    them in production.
  </p>

  <h2>No affiliation with n8n GmbH</h2>
  <p>
    "n8n" is a trademark of n8n GmbH. This Site is an independent publisher and is not affiliated
    with, endorsed by, or sponsored by n8n GmbH. References to n8n are nominative and used solely to
    identify the platform our workflows target.
  </p>

  <h2>Third-party integrations</h2>
  <p>
    Many workflows integrate with third-party providers (OpenAI, Anthropic, Apify, ElevenLabs,
    HeyGen, Twilio, Google Workspace, Meta APIs, etc.). Our content is not an endorsement of any
    provider, and pricing or behavior of those services may change without notice. You are
    responsible for reviewing each provider's terms before use.
  </p>

  <h2>Accuracy</h2>
  <p>
    n8n evolves quickly. Docker tags, node names, AI integrations, and platform pricing change. We
    make reasonable efforts to keep guides current, but some details may become outdated between
    publication and your visit. When in doubt, cross-check with official sources at
    <a href="https://docs.n8n.io" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">docs.n8n.io</a>.
  </p>

  <h2>Advertising</h2>
  <p>
    Advertisements may appear on Site pages via Google AdSense or similar networks. Ad placements
    are not editorial endorsements. See our
    <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a> for details on ad cookies and opt-out options.
  </p>

  <h2>Liability</h2>
  <p>
    We are not liable for losses arising from use of workflows, including but not limited to API
    cost overruns, account suspensions on third-party platforms, data loss, or business interruption.
    See <a href="/terms">Terms of Use</a> for the full liability section.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    Spotted an inaccuracy? Email <a href={`mailto:${SITE.email}`}>{SITE.email}</a> with the page URL
    and the correction. We update corrections promptly.
  </p>
</GuideLayout>
